{
  "stem": "979.4",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And also, they ruined two gas chambers.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They blew up the gas chambers.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The-- the Greeks?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The Greeks.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There were five of them.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And, of course, they-- they punished them at the end.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I think I have something on them.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I say, the one who did it-- I don't know if he's alive, if he made it.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But they-- after-- they-- they now, the Nazis-- oh, not the Nazis, the British are coming closer.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They knew, now, it's coming to an end.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Because the men knew from other people.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Sometimes they used to work outdoors, and a political person knew passed, and they would tell them that we're coming to an end.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "It's coming to an end.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "It's gonna end soon.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Because as the British was coming closer and closer-- oh, we're hoping that we make it.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And-- and suddenly, we see all these men going.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And now we don't know anymore what happened to my brother.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And-- and then we continue now, something happened very bad to us, the orchestra, in the meantime.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Now, I told you, the-- the block leader was Alma Rose, the-- that famous person.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And she-- now there were also, as I say, there were also German prisoners who were real Germans.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "For political reasons they were there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "There was one, Frau Smith, one German woman who made friends with Alma Rose.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Now she met her, they both speak German.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "So they decided that she had a nice little bungalow for her own-- whatever she was, whatever she lived.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "She lived in the camp.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "Maybe she had a better room than everybody else.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And she brought-- she invited Alma Rose always to have, every Sunday, to have dinner at her house together.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "She had more food, and that, and more privilege.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
